EXCUSE ME.
I'M LOOKING FOR DANA SCULLY.
IS SHE A PATIENT HERE ?

6
00:00:25,625 --> 00:00:28,161
DANA SCULLY ?

7
00:00:28,161 --> 00:00:31,164
IS-IS THERE
AN ADMITTING NURSE HERE ?

8
00:00:31,164 --> 00:00:34,167
