HELP ME HERE ?
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO CALM DOWN.

9
00:00:34,167 --> 00:00:36,953
I WILL CALM DOWN
WHEN SOMEBODY GIVES ME
A REASON TO CALM DOWN !

10
00:00:37,454 --> 00:00:40,373
NOW, I'M LOOKING FOR A PATIENT
THAT WAS ADMITTED TO THE E.R.
DANA SCULLY.

11
00:00:40,373 --> 00:00:42,842
YES !
WHERE IS SHE ?
I HEARD YOU THE FIRST TIME.

12
00:00:42,842 --> 00:00:44,911
I HAVE HER IN THE I.C.U.
WHERE IS THAT ?

13
00:00:44,911 --> 00:00:47,247
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO TELL ME
WHO YOU ARE FIRST.
WHERE IS SHE ?

14
00:00:47,247 --> 00:00:48,915
AGENT MULDER !

15
00:00:52,052 --> 00:00:54,054
WHERE YOU GOIN' ?
I.C.U.

16
00:00:54,054 --> 00:00:56,556
YOU'RE MOVIN' PRETTY GOOD
FOR A DEAD MAN.
I'M ONLY HALF DEAD.

17
00:00:56,556 --> 00:00:58,942
YOU GOT A LOT TO ANSWER FOR,
AGENT MULDER !

18
00:01:00,443 --> 00:01:02,779
YOU GUYS HOLD HERE.
YES, SIR.

19
00:01:17,744 --> 00:01:21,047
WHAT HAPPENED TO HER ?
SHE WENT INTO
HYPOVOLEMIC SHOCK.

20
00:01:21,047 --> 00:01:23,249
SHE'S LOST A LOT OF BLOOD.

21
00:01:23,249 --> 00:01:25,051
DUE TO WHAT ?

22
00:01:26,386 --> 00:01:29,472
DUE TO WHAT ?
SHE'S DYING.

23
00:01:31,958 --> 00:01:35,428
LET'S GO HOME.
THERE'S NOTHING YOU CAN DO.
LET GO OF ME.

24
00:01:35,428 --> 00:01:37,397
GET THE HELL OFF OF ME !
DON'T DO THIS !

25
00:01:37,897 --> 00:01:40,316
DON'T MAKE ME PUT YOU
UNDER ARREST.  DON'T !

26
00:02:40,309 --> 00:02:42,528
[ Blevins ]
I'M SOMEWHAT AT A LOSS HERE
IN GOING FORWARD.

27
00:02:44,797 --> 00:02:47,717
THIS SITUATION
DEVELOPING UNEXPECTEDLY...

28
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:51,971
DURING A FORMAL INQUIRY
INTO YOUR REPORTED DEATH,
AGENT MULDER.

29
00:02:51,971 --> 00:02:55,841
THE FACT OF YOUR BEING HERE
TODAY VERY MUCH ALIVE,

30
00:02:55,841 --> 00:02:59,211
IT GIVES THE EFFECT OF
RESHAPING THIS INVESTIGATION...

31
00:02:59,712 --> 00:03:01,497
INTO SOMETHING
ALTOGETHER DIFFERENT,

32
00:03:01,497 --> 00:03:04,283
AS WE'RE NOW PUT UPON
TO VERIFY THE IDENTITY...

33
00:03:04,283 --> 00:03:06,285
OF THIS BODY
FOUND IN YOUR APARTMENT...

34
00:03:06,786 --> 00:03:08,788
AND THE CIRCUMSTANCES
WHICH LED TO THIS.

35
00:03:09,288 --> 00:03:11,157
WOULD YOU CARE TO ENLIGHTEN US
ON THESE CIRCUMSTANCES ?

36
00:03:11,157 --> 00:03:14,026
ARE YOU SUGGESTING
THAT I CAN ?
[ Blevins ]  AGENT MULDER,

37
00:03:14,026 --> 00:03:17,313
WE'RE HERE INFORMALLY
TO GIVE YOU THE CHANCE
TO HELP YOURSELF.

38
00:03:17,313 --> 00:03:19,265
HELP MYSELF HOW ?

39
00:03:19,765 --> 00:03:22,351
BY ALLOWING ANY FACTS OR DETAILS
WHICH MIGHT SERVE...

40
00:03:22,835 --> 00:03:25,604
TO LET US GO FORWARD
WITH THIS INQUIRY
IN A MORE INFORMED MANNER.

41
00:03:25,604 --> 00:03:27,973
THAT HELPS YOU.
HOW DOES THAT HELP ME ?

42
00:03:27,973 --> 00:03:31,477
[ Blevins ]  AGENT MULDER,
THIS IS GOING TO QUICKLY
BECOME A MURDER INVESTIGATION.

43
00:03:31,477 --> 00:03:33,446
CRIMINAL CHARGES
ARE GOING TO BE MADE.

44
00:03:33,446 --> 00:03:35,748
[ Skinner ]
WE HAVE ONLY ONE OTHER SUSPECT.

45
00:03:35,748 --> 00:03:38,017
SHE MAY NO LONGER BE ABLE
TO TESTIFY ON HER OWN BEHALF.

46
00:03:38,017 --> 00:03:41,520
AGENT SCULLY LIED TO US.
WHY ?

47
00:03:43,205 --> 00:03:47,460
WHO'S PROTECTING WHOM,
AGENT MULDER ?

48
00:03:47,460 --> 00:03:49,478
[ Blevins ]
YOUR CHOICE IS YOUR OWN,
BUT YOUR FAILURE TO ANSWER...

49
00:03:49,478 --> 00:03:52,231
WILL REFLECT POORLY ON
THE RECORD IN A FORMAL INQUIRY.

50
00:03:53,933 --> 00:03:56,702
ARE WE FINISHED THEN ?

51
00:04:02,007 --> 00:04:04,193
[ Door Opens ]

52
00:04:04,193 --> 00:04:06,512
[ Door Closes ]

53
00:04:09,448 --> 00:04:12,952
WORD OF ADVICE, MY FRIEND.
KEEP PLAYIN' IT THE WAY YOU ARE.

54
00:04:12,952 --> 00:04:15,471
THANKS, BUDDY.
HEY, RIGHT NOW,
YOU NEED A BUDDY.

55
00:04:15,471 --> 00:04:17,473
YOU NEED ALL THE HELP
 YOU CAN GET.

56
00:04:17,473 --> 00:04:19,475
YOU SHOULD'VE MENTIONED
THAT AT THE HOSPITAL,
HAULING MY ASS OFF.

57
00:04:19,475 --> 00:04:21,777
I SAVED YOUR ASS,
AGENT MULDER.

58
00:04:21,777 --> 00:04:25,498
I'VE BEEN WITHHOLDING
FORENSIC EVIDENCE ABOUT THE BODY
FOUND ON YOUR APARTMENT FLOOR.

59
00:04:25,498 --> 00:04:28,317
UNTIL YOU SHOWED UP LAST NIGHT,
I WAS THE ONE
KEEPING YOUR SECRET.

60
00:04:28,317 --> 00:04:30,119
I HAD NO CHOICE
BUT TO BRING YOU IN.

61
00:04:30,119 --> 00:04:32,388
SCULLY WILL VERIFY
ALL OF THAT.

62
00:04:32,388 --> 00:04:35,624
THAT'S A GOOD PLACE TO LAY IT,
CONSIDERING HER CONDITION.

63
00:04:35,624 --> 00:04:38,344
YOU WANT ME TO LAY IT
WHERE IT BELONGS, AGENT MULDER ?

64
00:04:38,344 --> 00:04:42,114
PATHOLOGY TURNED UP
TWO GUNSHOT WOUNDS TO
THE DEAD MAN IN YOUR APARTMENT--

65
00:04:42,114 --> 00:04:44,967
ONE FIRED POINT-BLANK
TO THE LEFT TEMPLE
WITH A HANDGUN,

66
00:04:44,967 --> 00:04:47,703
THE SECOND A POSTMORTEM WOUND
TO THE FACE TO REMOVE
THE MAN'S IDENTITY.

67
00:04:49,705 --> 00:04:53,008
NOW, I'D BE HAPPY
TO VERIFY THE BALLISTICS
ON THAT FIRST SHOT.

68
00:04:56,996 --> 00:04:59,131
HOW CAN YOU HELP ME ?

69
00:05:01,133 --> 00:05:02,968
TELL ME WHY
SCULLY LIED FOR YOU.

70
00:05:08,874 --> 00:05:12,912
THE DISEASE SHE HAS
WAS GIVEN TO HER...

71
00:05:12,912 --> 00:05:16,498
BY SOMEBODY CONNECTED
TO THE F.B.I.
TO A MOLE WORKING HERE.

72
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:20,302
WHO ?

73
00:05:20,302 --> 00:05:23,022
I FAILED TO
FIND THAT OUT, SIR.

74
00:05:30,329 --> 00:05:33,699
YOU DON'T WANT TO FORGET
WHO YOUR FRIENDS ARE,
AGENT MULDER--

75
00:05:33,699 --> 00:05:36,018
TO REMEMBER
WHO YOU CAN TRUST.

76
00:05:41,674 --> 00:05:44,677
[ Man On TV ]  THE CHAIRMAN
SAID, "WHAT ARE THE APPROPRIATE
LIMITS OF HUMAN KNOWLEDGE ?"

77
00:05:44,677 --> 00:05:47,980
I DON'T THINK THERE ARE
ANY APPROPRIATE LIMITS
TO HUMAN KNOWLEDGE.

78
00:05:47,980 --> 00:05:53,619
AS LONG AS SCIENCE
IS DONE OPENLY
AND WITH FREE WILL,

79
00:05:53,619 --> 00:05:55,721
THEN I DON'T THINK
THERE ARE ANY LIMITS.

80
00:05:55,721 --> 00:05:57,740
[ Man #2 ]
SENATOR KENNEDY.
[ Kennedy ]  DR. VERMONT,

81
00:05:57,740 --> 00:06:00,226
YOU'VE STATED THAT...

82
00:06:00,226 --> 00:06:02,895
THE CLONING OF HUMANS
WOULD BE ILL-CONSIDERED...

83
00:06:02,895 --> 00:06:04,897
AND TECHNICALLY DIFFICULT
TO ACCOMPLISH.

84
00:06:04,897 --> 00:06:08,400
CAN YOU EXPAND A LITTLE BIT
ON WHAT YOU SEE...

85
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:11,553
AS THE BIGGEST TECHNICAL
OBSTACLE TO HUMAN CLONING--

86
00:06:11,553 --> 00:06:13,539
[ Continues, Indistinct ]

87
00:06:16,058 --> 00:06:18,060
I TRUST YOU'VE HEARD.

88
00:06:18,060 --> 00:06:20,462
MULDER IS ALIVE.

89
00:06:22,848 --> 00:06:26,118
AS I SAID, HE'S NOT
TO BE UNDERESTIMATED.

90
00:06:26,118 --> 00:06:28,454
YES, AS YOU SAID.

91
00:06:28,454 --> 00:06:31,824
THOUGH I HEAR HE HAS YOU
TO THANK IN SOME PART
FOR HIS NEW FREEDOM.

92
00:06:31,824 --> 00:06:34,226
USING A STOLEN I.D.,

93
00:06:34,226 --> 00:06:37,596
MULDER WAS ABLE TO GET INSIDE
THE ADVANCED RESEARCH
PROJECTS FACILITY.

94
00:06:37,596 --> 00:06:40,032
AND YOU ALLOWED HIM TO ESCAPE.

95
00:06:40,032 --> 00:06:43,369
YES.
WE'RE TOO VULNERABLE.

96
00:06:45,304 --> 00:06:46,805
OUR MAN IN THE F.B.I.
IS EXPOSED.

97
00:06:46,805 --> 00:06:50,776
WHAT MULDER MAY HAVE SEEN
COULD EXPOSE OUR PLANS.

98
00:06:50,776 --> 00:06:54,280
WHAT MULDER'S SEEN
ONLY SERVES US.

99
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:56,649
IT SERVES TO ENSURE
OUR PLANS.

100
00:07:00,803 --> 00:07:02,805
MULDER'S IN TROUBLE.

101
00:07:02,805 --> 00:07:05,674
HE NEEDS HELP.
WE CAN GIVE IT TO HIM.

102
00:07:07,609 --> 00:07:09,495
IN EXCHANGE FOR ?

103
00:07:10,996 --> 00:07:13,999
HIS NEW LOYALTY...
TO US.

104
00:07:15,467 --> 00:07:17,469
AS I'VE SAID ALL ALONG,

105
00:07:17,469 --> 00:07:21,240
MULDER'S MUCH MORE VALUABLE
TO US ALIVE.

106
00:07:29,081 --> 00:07:31,083
YOU CAN PROCEED NOW.

107
00:07:43,662 --> 00:07:46,165
MULDER,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE ?

108
00:07:46,665 --> 00:07:48,400
HEARD YOU WERE BEING
MOVED OUT OF I.C.U.,
YOU WERE FEELING BETTER.

109
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:51,453
MULDER, SOMEBODY'S
GONNA SEE YOU HERE.
IT'S OKAY.

110
00:07:53,238 --> 00:07:55,624
I'M OFFICIALLY AMONG
THE UNDEAD.

111
00:07:55,624 --> 00:07:58,577
WHAT HAPPENED ?

112
00:07:58,577 --> 00:08:00,412
I DIDN'T COME HERE
TO TALK ABOUT THAT.

113
00:08:00,412 --> 00:08:04,166
MULDER, DON'T TRY
AND PROTECT ME.
I NEED TO KNOW.

114
00:08:04,166 --> 00:08:06,952
WELL, THERE'S NOT MUCH
TO TALK ABOUT ANYWAY.

115
00:08:06,952 --> 00:08:10,456
I'M GONNA TESTIFY
TO EVERYTHING I KNOW IN FRONT
OF THE F.B.I. ASSEMBLY.

116
00:08:10,456 --> 00:08:13,792
THE CONSPIRACY,
THE MEN BEHIND IT,
WHAT I BELIEVE IS ITS PURPOSE.

117
00:08:13,792 --> 00:08:16,645
DID YOU FIND OUT WHO
IN THE F.B.I. IS INVOLVED ?

118
00:08:16,645 --> 00:08:19,314
NO.  BUT THAT
DOESN'T MATTER NOW.

119
00:08:19,314 --> 00:08:22,768
YES, IT DOES.
HEY, SCULLY,
HOW ABOUT THOSE YANKEES, HUH ?

120
00:08:22,768 --> 00:08:26,205
MULDER, SKINNER HAS EVIDENCE
AGAINST YOU.

121
00:08:26,205 --> 00:08:28,957
HE KNOWS THAT YOU KILLED
THAT MAN THEY FOUND
IN YOUR APARTMENT.

122
00:08:28,957 --> 00:08:31,543
YEAH.
SKINNER'S WITHHOLDING IT.

123
00:08:31,543 --> 00:08:34,947
MULDER, SKINNER'S DIRTY.
HE'S NOT YOUR FRIEND.

124
00:08:34,947 --> 00:08:37,249
I'M ALMOST CERTAIN THAT
HE'S THE MAN INSIDE ON THIS.

125
00:08:37,249 --> 00:08:39,568
I DON'T BELIEVE THAT.

126
00:08:39,568 --> 00:08:43,489
IF YOU TESTIFY,
HE WILL USE IT TO RUIN YOU.

127
00:08:45,274 --> 00:08:47,076
NO, NOT SKINNER.

128
00:08:47,076 --> 00:08:50,946
HE'S-HE'S BEEN IN A POSITION
TO KNOW EVERYTHING
FROM THE BEGINNING,

129
00:08:50,946 --> 00:08:52,831
EVERYTHING THAT WE'VE DONE
OVER THE PAST FOUR YEARS.

130
00:08:52,831 --> 00:08:55,801
IF I DON'T TESTIFY NOW,
THEY'LL START TO BURY THE TRUTH.

131
00:09:03,108 --> 00:09:04,910
WELL, THEN YOU HAVE TO
LAY IT ON ME.

132
00:09:04,910 --> 00:09:06,745
YOU HAVE TO TELL THEM...

133
00:09:07,212 --> 00:09:08,997
THAT I WAS THE ONE
WHO KILLED THAT MAN.

134
00:09:13,352 --> 00:09:14,853
I CAN'T--
 I CAN'T DO THAT.

135
00:09:14,853 --> 00:09:17,806
YES, YOU CAN.

136
00:09:17,806 --> 00:09:19,641
MULDER, IF I CAN SAVE YOU,
LET ME.

137
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:25,380
LET ME AT LEAST
GIVE SOME MEANING
TO WHAT'S HAPPENED TO ME.

138
00:09:27,466 --> 00:09:29,635
[ Door Opens ]

139
00:09:29,635 --> 00:09:32,754
DANA ?  HI, FOX.
HI, MRS. SCULLY.

140
00:09:32,754 --> 00:09:35,441
- I HOPE I'M NOT INTERRUPTING.
- NO, NO, NO.

141
00:09:35,441 --> 00:09:37,276
I WAS JUST ON MY WAY OUT.

142
00:09:45,918 --> 00:09:48,420
HI.  I'M, UH--
I'M FOX MULDER.
I DON'T THINK WE'VE EVER MET.

143
00:09:48,921 --> 00:09:50,923
I'M BILL SCULLY.

144
00:09:52,908 --> 00:09:55,160
I'M SORRY
ABOUT YOUR SISTER.

145
00:09:56,495 --> 00:09:58,780
MR. MULDER.
YEAH ?

146
00:10:00,282 --> 00:10:02,034
I KNOW SOMETHING ABOUT YOU--

147
00:10:02,534 --> 00:10:04,736
ABOUT WHAT DANA'S
BEEN THROUGH WITH YOU, SO...

148
00:10:04,736 --> 00:10:07,672
LET'S LEAVE THE WORK
AWAY FROM HERE, OKAY ?

149
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:12,210
LET HER DIE WITH DIGNITY.

150
00:11:03,728 --> 00:11:06,898
PLEASE TELL ME YOU'RE HERE
WITH SEVERE CHEST PAINS.

151
00:11:06,898 --> 00:11:10,084
YOU SHOULD BE GLAD
FOR WHY I'M HERE--
TO PAY YOU SOME RESPECT.

152
00:11:10,084 --> 00:11:13,170
GO TO HELL.
FOR YOUR CLEVERNESS
AND YOUR RESOURCE,

153
00:11:13,671 --> 00:11:15,172
WHAT YOU MANAGED
TO DO FOR SCULLY.

154
00:11:15,172 --> 00:11:17,959
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT ?

155
00:11:17,959 --> 00:11:22,246
WELL, BREACHING THE SECURITY
AT THE DEFENSE DEPARTMENT
FACILITY,

156
00:11:22,246 --> 00:11:24,081
FINDING THE CURE
FOR HER DISEASE.

157
00:11:24,081 --> 00:11:28,185
WHAT I FOUND WAS USELESS.
ON THE CONTRARY.

158
00:11:28,185 --> 00:11:30,354
IT'S ESSENTIAL
TO HER SURVIVAL.

159
00:11:33,608 --> 00:11:36,611
IF YOU LIKE,
WE COULD STEP OUTSIDE
AND I MIGHT EXPLAIN MYSELF.

160
00:11:39,814 --> 00:11:42,416
I'M HERE TONIGHT AS A FRIEND,
AGENT MULDER.

161
00:11:56,797 --> 00:11:59,800
HE PROMISED ME
IT WOULD BE IN HERE.

162
00:12:12,163 --> 00:12:14,131
[ Frohike ]
I'LL BE DAMNED.

163
00:12:14,131 --> 00:12:17,735
IT NEVER OCCURRED TO ME
WHAT THE DEIONIZED WATER
MIGHT BE FOR.

164
00:12:17,735 --> 00:12:20,571
- WHO KNEW IT WAS A MICROCHIP
  WE WERE LOOKIN' FOR.
- THIS IS A CURE FOR CANCER ?

165
00:12:22,556 --> 00:12:25,559
- IT MAY BE FOR SCULLY'S.
- HOW ?

166
00:12:25,559 --> 00:12:27,345
[ Mulder ]
SHORTLY AFTER SHE WAS ABDUCTED,

167
00:12:27,345 --> 00:12:31,716
SHE DISCOVERED A SMALL
METALLIC CHIP IMPLANTED
SUBCUTANEOUSLY IN HER NECK.

168
00:12:31,716 --> 00:12:35,503
IT WAS JUST A SHORT TIME
AFTER SHE HAD IT REMOVED
THAT SHE DEVELOPED CANCER.

169
00:12:35,503 --> 00:12:38,205
- IT'S UNREAL.
- TOO FREAKIN' AMAZING.

170
00:12:38,205 --> 00:12:41,776
WATCH YOUR LANGUAGE, FROHIKE,
AND GRAB ME SOME TWEEZERS.

171
00:13:03,147 --> 00:13:05,533
[ Blevins ]
MR. KRITSCHGAU, THANK YOU
FOR BEING HERE TODAY...

172
00:13:05,533 --> 00:13:07,752
AND FOR COOPERATING
WITH THIS INVESTIGATION.

173
00:13:07,752 --> 00:13:10,621
WE HOPE YOU CAN
PROVIDE INFORMATION...

174
00:13:10,621 --> 00:13:12,823
THAT WILL ALLOW US
TO MAKE FORMAL CHARGES...

175
00:13:12,823 --> 00:13:15,876
FOR THE MURDER OF DEFENSE
EMPLOYEE SCOTT OSTELHOFF.

176
00:13:15,876 --> 00:13:17,862
MR. KRITSCHGAU,

177
00:13:17,862 --> 00:13:21,499
WE HAVE LEARNED THAT
YOU WERE IN CONTACT WITH
AGENTS MULDER AND SCULLY...

178
00:13:21,499 --> 00:13:23,317
JUST PRIOR TO THIS MAN'S DEATH.

179
00:13:23,317 --> 00:13:27,772
- THAT'S CORRECT.
- AND THAT YOU MAY HAVE GIVEN
  THEM CLASSIFIED INFORMATION.

180
00:13:29,607 --> 00:13:32,309
WHAT MOTIVATED THIS ?

181
00:13:32,309 --> 00:13:36,013
MY KNOWLEDGE OF GOVERNMENT
INVOLVEMENT IN A CONSPIRACY
AGAINST THE AMERICAN PEOPLE.

182
00:13:40,468 --> 00:13:42,970
UH, BEFORE--

183
00:13:42,970 --> 00:13:45,856
BEFORE WE GO INTO
ANY SPECIFICS ON THAT SUBJECT,

184
00:13:45,856 --> 00:13:48,843
I'D LIKE TO ASK YOU
A MORE POINTED QUESTION.

185
00:13:48,843 --> 00:13:51,128
DO YOU KNOW WHO KILLED
SCOTT OSTELHOFF ?

186
00:13:53,364 --> 00:13:55,015
NO, I DON'T.

187
00:13:55,015 --> 00:14:00,488
DO YOU KNOW OF ANY CONNECTION
BETWEEN HIS DEATH
AND AGENTS MULDER OR SCULLY ?

188
00:14:00,488 --> 00:14:03,641
NO.

189
00:14:04,141 --> 00:14:06,026
I'M AWARE OF ONE DEATH
IN CONNECTION, THOUGH.

190
00:14:09,497 --> 00:14:11,999
MY SON,
WHO DIED EARLY THIS MORNING.

191
00:14:16,470 --> 00:14:18,973
MR. KRITSCHGAU,

192
00:14:18,973 --> 00:14:21,475
YOU'RE EMPLOYED BY
THE DEPARTMENT OF DEFENSE,
IS THAT CORRECT ?

193
00:14:21,475 --> 00:14:23,344
[ Kritschgau ]
TECHNICALLY.

194
00:14:23,344 --> 00:14:27,281
PART OF MY REMUNERATION
HAS COME FROM ANOTHER SOURCE.

195
00:14:28,783 --> 00:14:32,169
A CONGRESSIONAL LOBBYING FIRM--
SOMETHING CALLED ROUSH.

196
00:14:34,722 --> 00:14:38,175
ROUSH ?
ANY IDEA WHAT THAT IS ?

197
00:14:38,175 --> 00:14:39,877
NO, SIR.

198
00:14:46,050 --> 00:14:48,936
THIS IS CRAZY, JUST CRAZY.

199
00:14:48,936 --> 00:14:51,739
WELL, CRAZY IN WHAT SENSE ?
IN THAT IT MIGHT SAVE
YOUR SISTER'S LIFE ?

200
00:14:51,739 --> 00:14:55,893
YOU'RE NOT A DOCTOR.
YOU HAVE NO PLACE EVEN
SUGGESTING THIS SCIENCE FICTION.

201
00:14:55,893 --> 00:14:59,330
IT'S NOT SCIENCE FICTION.
HE'S NEVER HEARD OF IT !

202
00:14:59,330 --> 00:15:01,832
BILL.
[ Sighs ]

203
00:15:03,334 --> 00:15:06,320
- HAVE YOU ?
- NO, I HAVEN'T.

204
00:15:06,320 --> 00:15:09,857
I THINK THERE'S AN OBVIOUS
DIFFERENCE OF OPINION HERE.

205
00:15:09,857 --> 00:15:12,459
[ Scully ]
I THINK...

206
00:15:12,459 --> 00:15:16,096
THAT EVERYBODY HERE HAS
THEIR HEART IN THE RIGHT PLACE.

207
00:15:18,833 --> 00:15:21,068
BUT I NEED IT
TO BE MY DECISION.

208
00:15:21,068 --> 00:15:24,288
DANA--
I KNOW YOU'RE ONLY
LOOKING OUT FOR ME, BILL,

209
00:15:24,288 --> 00:15:27,424
BUT I DON'T THINK
YOU HAVE ALL THE FACTS.

210
00:15:30,461 --> 00:15:32,630
DON'T YOU THINK YOU SHOULD
LISTEN TO YOUR DOCTOR ?

211
00:15:32,630 --> 00:15:36,050
YES.  I AM.

212
00:15:36,050 --> 00:15:38,302
WOULD SHE HAVE TO STOP
HER CONVENTIONAL TREATMENT ?

213
00:15:38,302 --> 00:15:40,721
[ Doctor ]
TO BE HONEST,
AT THIS POINT...

214
00:15:40,721 --> 00:15:44,141
THE ONLY APPROACH I HAVE LEFT
WITH HER PARTICULAR CANCER...

215
00:15:44,141 --> 00:15:46,143
IS QUITE UNCONVENTIONAL.

216
00:15:52,449 --> 00:15:54,285
I'D LIKE TO TRY THIS.

217
00:16:49,139 --> 00:16:51,141
YOU REALLY BELIEVE
THIS CRAP, DON'T YOU ?

218
00:16:51,141 --> 00:16:53,460
YES, I DO.

219
00:16:56,263 --> 00:16:58,766
YOU SEE,
SHE'S YOUR BIG DEFENDER,

220
00:16:58,766 --> 00:17:03,020
BUT I THINK THE TRUTH IS
SHE JUST DOESN'T WANT
TO DISAPPOINT YOU.

221
00:17:06,373 --> 00:17:09,209
IF IT WORKS, I DON'T CARE
WHAT YOU THINK SHE THINKS.

222
00:17:10,644 --> 00:17:13,147
YOU'RE A REAL PIECE OF WORK,
YOU KNOW THAT, MR. MULDER ?

223
00:17:13,647 --> 00:17:15,532
WHY IS THAT ?
BECAUSE I DON'T THINK
THE WAY YOU THINK ?

224
00:17:15,532 --> 00:17:19,853
BECAUSE I WON'T JUST SIT
PASSIVELY BACK AND WATCH
THE FAMILY TRAGEDY UNFOLD ?

225
00:17:19,853 --> 00:17:22,706
YOU'RE THE REASON FOR IT.

226
00:17:25,142 --> 00:17:28,979
AND I'VE ALREADY LOST ONE SISTER
TO THIS QUEST YOU'RE ON.

227
00:17:28,979 --> 00:17:31,332
NOW I'M LOSING ANOTHER.

228
00:17:37,338 --> 00:17:39,840
HAS IT BEEN WORTH IT ?

229
00:17:39,840 --> 00:17:42,343
I'LL TELL YOU WHAT I MEAN.
HAVE YOU FOUND
WHAT YOU'VE BEEN LOOKING FOR ?

230
00:17:47,314 --> 00:17:50,584
- NO.
- NO.

231
00:17:51,085 --> 00:17:52,586
YOU KNOW HOW
THAT MAKES ME FEEL ?

232
00:17:54,088 --> 00:17:56,090
IN A WAY, I THINK I DO.

233
00:17:56,090 --> 00:17:59,560
I LOST SOMEONE
VERY CLOSE TO ME.

234
00:18:00,561 --> 00:18:03,063
I LOST A SISTER.

235
00:18:03,063 --> 00:18:05,065
I LOST MY FATHER.

236
00:18:06,567 --> 00:18:09,320
ALL BECAUSE OF THIS THING
I'M LOOKING FOR.

237
00:18:09,320 --> 00:18:13,156
THIS WHAT ?
LITTLE GREEN ALIENS ?

238
00:18:19,930 --> 00:18:23,266
YEAH.
LITTLE GREEN ALIENS.

239
00:18:24,634 --> 00:18:26,470
YOU'RE ONE SORRY
SON OF A BITCH.

240
00:18:31,258 --> 00:18:33,543
THERE'S NOT A LOT MORE TO SAY.

241
00:18:40,417 --> 00:18:42,419
[ Cell Phone Ringing ]

242
00:18:48,925 --> 00:18:50,810
ONE SORRY
SON OF A BITCH SPEAKING.

243
00:18:50,810 --> 00:18:53,146
HOW'S OUR PATIENT ?

244
00:18:53,146 --> 00:18:56,883
YOU DID FIND THE CHIP,
DIDN'T YOU, AGENT MULDER ?
YES.

245
00:18:56,883 --> 00:19:00,187
I CAN IMAGINE
THERE WAS SOME QUESTION
AS TO ITS MEDICAL VALUE.

246
00:19:00,187 --> 00:19:03,139
WELL, THERE STILL IS.

247
00:19:03,139 --> 00:19:08,061
AND SO I HAVE YET
TO EARN YOUR TRUST,
IN SPITE OF MY GESTURE.

248
00:19:08,061 --> 00:19:12,065
[ Chuckles ]
YOU COULD SAY THAT, YEAH.

249
00:19:12,065 --> 00:19:13,900
WELL, I HAVE SOMETHING ELSE
TO OFFER YOU.

250
00:19:13,900 --> 00:19:17,837
I'VE ARRANGED A MEETING
I THINK YOU'LL WANT TO ATTEND,
MR. MULDER.

251
00:19:31,234 --> 00:19:33,503
TABASCO.
IT CURES ANYTHING.

252
00:19:34,988 --> 00:19:36,990
I'LL KEEP THAT IN MIND.

253
00:20:00,213 --> 00:20:01,965
YOU KNOW HIM OR SOMETHIN' ?

254
00:20:04,818 --> 00:20:07,237
I THINK THAT'S MY SISTER.

255
00:20:21,918 --> 00:20:24,621
SAMANTHA ?

256
00:20:39,986 --> 00:20:42,489
I WAS AFRAID
I'D NEVER SEE YOU AGAIN.

257
00:20:44,407 --> 00:20:48,712
HE ALWAYS TOLD ME SOMETHING
HAD HAPPENED TO YOU THAT NIGHT.

258
00:20:48,712 --> 00:20:52,082
WHO ?
 WHO TOLD YOU THAT ?

259
00:20:52,082 --> 00:20:54,985
MY FATHER.

260
00:21:09,933 --> 00:21:12,435
I NEVER REALLY KNEW
WHAT HAPPENED.

261
00:21:14,437 --> 00:21:18,274
I COULD NEVER PUT THE MEMORIES
ALL BACK TOGETHER.

262
00:21:18,274 --> 00:21:21,678
BUT AS MUCH
AS I TRIED TO REMEMBER,

263
00:21:21,678 --> 00:21:24,180
I TRIED MORE TO FORGET.

264
00:21:24,180 --> 00:21:27,183
WHY ?
I WAS EIGHT YEARS OLD...

265
00:21:28,568 --> 00:21:31,071
AND FRIGHTENED TO DEATH.

266
00:21:31,071 --> 00:21:32,856
AND THEY TOLD ME
THAT I WAS AN ORPHAN.

267
00:21:34,207 --> 00:21:37,594
BUT YOU CALL THAT MAN
YOUR FATHER.

268
00:21:37,594 --> 00:21:40,330
SOMETIME LATER,

269
00:21:40,330 --> 00:21:42,332
I DON'T KNOW HOW LONG,

270
00:21:42,332 --> 00:21:45,335
MY FOSTER PARENTS TOOK ME
TO A HOTEL ROOM...

271
00:21:45,335 --> 00:21:47,170
AND SAID THAT I WAS
GONNA SEE MY FATHER.

272
00:21:48,571 --> 00:21:51,391
BUT YOU KNEW
WHO YOUR FATHER WAS.
I THOUGHT I KNEW.

273
00:21:53,309 --> 00:21:57,113
BUT HE TOLD ME THAT
IT HAD ALL BEEN A SECRET,

274
00:21:57,113 --> 00:21:59,399
AND THAT HE AND MOM...

275
00:21:59,399 --> 00:22:01,651
HADN'T TOLD ANYONE
TO PROTECT THE FAMILY.

276
00:22:03,987 --> 00:22:06,690
AND YOU BELIEVED THAT ?
HE WAS SO KIND TO ME.

277
00:22:06,690 --> 00:22:10,894
AND HE WAS THE ONLY ONE
I COULD REMEMBER
FROM BEFORE WHAT HAPPENED.

278
00:22:13,296 --> 00:22:15,582
YOU DON'T REMEMBER ANYTHING
ABOUT THAT NIGHT ?

279
00:22:15,582 --> 00:22:19,369
I REMEMBER...

280
00:22:19,369 --> 00:22:21,154
YOU.

281
00:22:25,709 --> 00:22:27,711
I REMEMBER SOMETHING.

282
00:22:29,713 --> 00:22:33,049
MEN, AND--
AND THEN NOTHING.

283
00:22:33,049 --> 00:22:34,951
I CAN HELP YOU.

284
00:22:38,521 --> 00:22:42,041
YOU WERE ABDUCTED, SAMANTHA.
I CAN HELP YOU TO REMEMBER.

285
00:22:42,041 --> 00:22:46,646
I DON'T WANT TO, FOX.
 I DON'T.

286
00:22:48,098 --> 00:22:49,933
THEN WHY COME HERE AT ALL ?

287
00:22:49,933 --> 00:22:52,585
MY FATHER TOLD ME
THAT HE'D FOUND YOU.

288
00:22:53,870 --> 00:22:56,239
YOU WANTED TO SEE ME
VERY BADLY--

289
00:22:56,239 --> 00:23:00,710
THAT YOU'D BEEN LOOKING
FOR ME FOR A LONG TIME.

290
00:23:03,012 --> 00:23:05,715
IS THAT TRUE ?

291
00:23:15,091 --> 00:23:17,877
I'M SO SORRY, FOX.

292
00:23:17,877 --> 00:23:20,713
AND I WISH THAT I'D KNOWN
HOW TO FIND YOU.

293
00:23:27,353 --> 00:23:31,574
WHAT YOU'VE BEEN TOLD--
I WANT YOU
TO LISTEN TO ME, OKAY ?

294
00:23:31,574 --> 00:23:33,877
WHAT YOU'VE BEEN TOLD
BY THAT MAN...

295
00:23:33,877 --> 00:23:36,029
MAY NOT BE TRUE.

296
00:23:36,029 --> 00:23:39,532
WHY DO YOU SAY THAT ?
BECAUSE THE MAN
THAT BROUGHT YOU HERE...

297
00:23:40,033 --> 00:23:41,901
HAS KNOWN WHERE I'VE BEEN
FOR A VERY LONG TIME.

298
00:23:41,901 --> 00:23:44,354
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

299
00:23:44,354 --> 00:23:46,239
WHY WOULDN'T HE TELL ME ?

300
00:23:46,239 --> 00:23:48,224
I DON'T KNOW.

301
00:23:48,725 --> 00:23:50,527
BUT I THINK HE'S KEPT
A LOT OF THINGS FROM YOU.

302
00:23:51,928 --> 00:23:56,683
I DON'T BELIEVE YOU.
HE'S BEEN A GOOD FATHER TO ME.

303
00:23:56,683 --> 00:24:00,386
HE'S GIVEN ME A LIFE,
AND HE CARED FOR ME
WHEN THERE WAS NO ONE ELSE.

304
00:24:00,386 --> 00:24:03,573
THEN I WANT YOU
TO COME WITH ME--
COME WITH ME TO SEE MOM.

305
00:24:07,510 --> 00:24:10,780
- MOM IS ALIVE ?
- YES.

306
00:24:13,016 --> 00:24:15,668
AND I KNOW SHE'D LIKE
TO SEE YOU VERY, VERY MUCH.

307
00:24:21,591 --> 00:24:24,494
- I CAN'T.
- WHY NOT ?

308
00:24:24,494 --> 00:24:28,698
THIS IS TOO MUCH.
I DIDN'T WANNA
COME HERE AT ALL, FOX.

309
00:24:28,698 --> 00:24:32,352
I WAS AFRAID TO SEE YOU.
 I HAVE ANOTHER LIFE NOW.

310
00:24:32,852 --> 00:24:34,771
I HAVE CHILDREN OF MY OWN.
DON'T--  NO.
NO, PLEASE DON'T GO.

311
00:24:34,771 --> 00:24:37,140
I CAN'T STAY HERE NOW.
TELL ME HOW I CAN FIND YOU.

312
00:24:37,140 --> 00:24:39,642
I NEED SOME TIME.
JUST-JUST TELL ME
WHERE I CAN FIND YOU.

313
00:24:39,642 --> 00:24:42,562
PLEASE DON'T, FOX !

314
00:24:44,264 --> 00:24:48,101
WE WILL DO THIS
ON YOUR TIME.  JUST--

315
00:24:48,101 --> 00:24:51,704
THEN PLEASE--
PLEASE LET ME GO.

316
00:25:05,935 --> 00:25:08,805
I PROMISE YOU
I'LL THINK ABOUT IT.

317
00:25:49,495 --> 00:25:51,497
[ Doctor ]
YOU DOING OKAY ?
[ Scully ]  MMM.

318
00:25:51,497 --> 00:25:54,000
EITHER IT'S MY HEAD
OR I'M A LONG WAY
FROM MED SCHOOL,

319
00:25:54,000 --> 00:25:55,919
BUT I CAN'T REMEMBER WHAT
YOU'RE INJECTING ME WITH.

320
00:25:55,919 --> 00:26:01,174
FLURO-DEOXYGLUCOSE.
DEOXYGLUCOSE.

321
00:26:01,174 --> 00:26:04,694
IF YOU'RE MAKING ANY PROGRESS,
I'M HOPING IT MIGHT SHOW UP
FIRST IN A PET SCAN.

322
00:26:06,361 --> 00:26:08,163
YOU'RE NOT HOLDING
YOUR BREATH, ARE YOU ?

323
00:26:08,163 --> 00:26:12,050
I'M GOING AFTER YOUR CANCER
AS AGGRESSIVELY AS
I KNOW HOW, DANA.

324
00:26:12,050 --> 00:26:15,437
IF I CAN JUMP-START
YOUR IMMUNE SYSTEM,

325
00:26:15,937 --> 00:26:18,957
IF I CAN GET YOUR CYTOLYTIC
CELLS TO RECOGNIZE YOUR TUMOR...

326
00:26:19,457 --> 00:26:22,878
AS SOMETHING TO ATTACK,
THEN THERE'S A CHANCE.

327
00:26:25,830 --> 00:26:28,550
HAVE YOU EVER WITNESSED
A MIRACLE, DR. ZUCKERMAN ?

328
00:26:29,885 --> 00:26:33,088
I DON'T KNOW THAT I HAVE.

329
00:26:33,088 --> 00:26:35,390
BUT I HAVE SEEN PEOPLE
MAKE RECOVERIES--

330
00:26:35,390 --> 00:26:38,493
COME BACK FROM SO FAR GONE,
I CAN'T EXPLAIN IT.

331
00:26:39,995 --> 00:26:41,997
ISN'T THAT A MIRACLE ?

332
00:26:44,499 --> 00:26:47,002
MAYBE THEY ARE MIRACLES,

333
00:26:47,002 --> 00:26:49,287
BUT I DON'T DARE
CALL THEM THAT.

334
00:26:51,556 --> 00:26:53,441
THANK YOU.

335
00:27:24,906 --> 00:27:27,409
MY APOLOGIES FOR THE...

336
00:27:27,409 --> 00:27:30,412
RATHER HASTY DEPARTURE
LAST NIGHT.
WHAT DO YOU WANT FROM ME ?

337
00:27:30,912 --> 00:27:33,415
WANT FROM YOU ?

338
00:27:33,415 --> 00:27:36,918
YOU GIVE ME THESE THINGS,
THE ONLY THINGS
I EVER WANTED,

339
00:27:36,918 --> 00:27:39,921
AND I CAN'T THINK
OF ANY REASON
FOR YOU TO DO SO.

340
00:27:39,921 --> 00:27:42,924
WELL, THAT'S TRUE.
NO ACT IS COMPLETELY SELFLESS.

341
00:27:44,426 --> 00:27:46,428
BUT I'VE COME TODAY NOT TO--

342
00:27:46,428 --> 00:27:49,431
NOT TO ASK BUT TO OFFER.

343
00:27:49,431 --> 00:27:52,934
OFFER YOU THE TRUTH THAT
YOU'VE SO DESPERATELY SOUGHT--

344
00:27:53,435 --> 00:27:57,188
ABOUT THE PROJECT,
ABOUT THE MEN
WHO'VE CONSPIRED TO PROTECT IT.

345
00:27:57,188 --> 00:28:01,142
I KNOW THE TRUTH.
DO YOU ?

346
00:28:01,142 --> 00:28:03,962
I SPOKE TO ONE OF YOUR MEN.
AND YOU KNOW
HE'S NOT A LIAR ?

347
00:28:03,962 --> 00:28:05,964
I'VE SEEN ENOUGH TO KNOW
HE'S NOT A LIAR, YEAH.

348
00:28:05,964 --> 00:28:08,750
YOU'VE SEEN BUT SCANT PIECES
OF THE WHOLE.

349
00:28:08,750 --> 00:28:11,302
WHAT MORE
CAN YOU SHOW ME ?

350
00:28:11,803 --> 00:28:14,606
THIS MAN YOU SPOKE TO,
MICHAEL KRITSCHGAU,

351
00:28:16,408 --> 00:28:18,743
HE'S DECEIVED YOU
WITH BEAUTIFUL LIES.

352
00:28:18,743 --> 00:28:21,179
HE'S TOLD YOU THAT EVERYTHING
YOU'VE EVER BELIEVED...

353
00:28:21,179 --> 00:28:23,515
ABOUT THE EXISTENCE
OF EXTRATERRESTRIAL LIFE
IS UNTRUE.

354
00:28:25,917 --> 00:28:27,819
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING ?

355
00:28:32,323 --> 00:28:35,326
AS I SAID,
I'M OFFERING YOU A CHANCE
TO KNOW THE TRUTH.

356
00:28:36,778 --> 00:28:38,530
IN EXCHANGE FOR WHAT ?

357
00:28:38,530 --> 00:28:41,049
QUIT THE F.B.I.
COME WORK FOR ME.

358
00:28:43,351 --> 00:28:44,853
YOU CAN MAKE YOUR PROBLEMS
GO AWAY.

359
00:28:51,359 --> 00:28:53,361
NO DEAL.

360
00:28:55,263 --> 00:28:57,348
AFTER ALL I'VE GIVEN YOU ?

361
00:28:57,348 --> 00:28:59,350
WHAT HAVE--
 WHAT HAVE YOU GIVEN ME ?

362
00:28:59,350 --> 00:29:01,853
THE CLAIM OF A CURE FOR SCULLY ?
IS SHE CURED ?

363
00:29:02,353 --> 00:29:04,773
YOU SHOW ME MY SISTER
ONLY TO TAKE HER RIGHT BACK ?
YOU'VE GIVEN ME NOTHING.

364
00:29:04,773 --> 00:29:08,309
I INTEND TO KEEP MY PROMISES.
 I JUST NEED SOMETHING FROM YOU.

365
00:29:08,727 --> 00:29:12,297
YOU MURDERED MY FATHER.
 YOU KILLED SCULLY'S SISTER.

366
00:29:12,297 --> 00:29:14,632
AND IF SCULLY DIES,
I WILL KILL YOU.

367
00:29:14,632 --> 00:29:16,818
I DON'T CARE
WHOSE FATHER YOU ARE.

368
00:29:16,818 --> 00:29:19,387
I WILL PUT YOU DOWN.

369
00:29:19,387 --> 00:29:22,741
WELL, YOU'RE CERTAINLY CAPABLE,
SO I'VE BEEN TOLD.

370
00:29:23,241 --> 00:29:24,743
I UNDERSTAND YOU HAVE
A HEARING TOMORROW,

371
00:29:24,743 --> 00:29:28,730
WHERE YOU'LL HAVE TO TESTIFY
TO THESE MURDEROUS IMPULSES
OF YOURS.

372
00:29:36,204 --> 00:29:38,206
WHEN YOU RECONSIDER,
THE OFFER STILL STANDS.

373
00:29:50,902 --> 00:29:52,403
[ Mrs. Scully ]
DANA ?

374
00:29:53,838 --> 00:29:56,341
DR. ZUCKERMAN CALLED.
HE, UH--

375
00:29:56,341 --> 00:29:58,843
HE SAID THAT
YOU WANTED TO SEE ME.

376
00:30:01,346 --> 00:30:03,348
WHAT IS IT ?

377
00:30:05,350 --> 00:30:07,852
[ Sobbing ]
I'M SO SORRY.

378
00:30:09,237 --> 00:30:12,240
I FIGHT AND I FIGHT...

379
00:30:12,240 --> 00:30:14,242
AND I FIGHT,

380
00:30:14,242 --> 00:30:16,744
BUT I'VE BEEN SO STUPID.

381
00:30:16,744 --> 00:30:19,497
WHAT ?  WHAT IS IT ?

382
00:30:23,785 --> 00:30:26,788
I'VE COME SO FAR IN MY LIFE
ON SIMPLE FAITH.

383
00:30:28,289 --> 00:30:31,126
AND NOW WHEN I NEED IT THE MOST,
I JUST PUSH IT AWAY.

384
00:30:33,478 --> 00:30:36,064
I MEAN, WHY--

385
00:30:36,064 --> 00:30:37,849
WHY DO I WEAR THIS ?

386
00:30:37,849 --> 00:30:39,868
WHY DO I WEAR THIS, MOM ?

387
00:30:41,553 --> 00:30:44,489
I PUT SOMETHING
THAT I DON'T EVEN KNOW...

388
00:30:44,989 --> 00:30:46,991
OR UNDERSTAND
UNDER THE SKIN OF MY NECK.

389
00:30:47,492 --> 00:30:49,494
I WILL SUBJECT MYSELF
TO THESE CRAZY TREATMENTS,

390
00:30:49,994 --> 00:30:54,782
AND I KEEP TELLING MYSELF
THAT I'M DOING EVERYTHING I CAN,
BUT IT'S A LIE.

391
00:30:54,782 --> 00:30:58,353
YOU HAVE NOT LOST
YOUR FAITH, DANA.

392
00:30:59,654 --> 00:31:02,157
BUT I HAVE... IN A WAY.

393
00:31:04,159 --> 00:31:07,662
WHEN YOU ASKED--
WHEN YOU ASKED FATHER McCUE
TO DINNER...

394
00:31:07,662 --> 00:31:09,664
TO MINISTER TO MY FAITH,

395
00:31:11,666 --> 00:31:13,501
I JUST CLOSED OFF TO HIM.

396
00:31:16,421 --> 00:31:17,922
WHAT'S IMPORTANT NOW...

397
00:31:19,424 --> 00:31:21,426
IS THAT
YOU SAVE YOUR ENERGY.

398
00:31:25,313 --> 00:31:27,148
I'M NOT GETTING BETTER, MOM.

399
00:31:27,148 --> 00:31:29,834
YOU DON'T KNOW THAT YET.

400
00:31:29,834 --> 00:31:32,554
THE PET SCAN
SHOWED NO IMPROVEMENT.

401
00:31:44,866 --> 00:31:47,769
I KNOW YOU'RE AFRAID.

402
00:31:51,172 --> 00:31:52,924
I KNOW YOU'RE AFRAID
TO TELL ME,

403
00:31:52,924 --> 00:31:55,009
BUT YOU HAVE TO
TELL SOMEONE.

404
00:31:59,747 --> 00:32:02,200
I'LL MAKE A STATEMENT
RIGHT HERE.

405
00:32:02,200 --> 00:32:05,169
CLONING WILL CONTINUE.

406
00:32:05,670 --> 00:32:08,172
THE HUMAN MIND WILL CONTINUE
TO INQUIRE INTO THIS.

407
00:32:09,674 --> 00:32:13,678
HUMAN CLONING WILL TAKE PLACE,
AND IT'LL TAKE PLACE
IN MY LIFETIME.

408
00:32:13,678 --> 00:32:16,931
I THINK IT'S RIGHT AND PROPER
THAT WE CONTINUE
THIS KIND OF INQUIRY.

409
00:32:16,931 --> 00:32:20,985
I THINK IT HOLDS UNTOLD BENEFITS
FOR HUMAN KIND.

410
00:32:20,985 --> 00:32:25,823
TURN ON YOUR TELEVISION.
ARE YOU WATCHING THE HEARINGS ?

411
00:32:25,823 --> 00:32:28,209
DO YOU SEE WHO'S THERE ?

412
00:32:28,209 --> 00:32:30,545
HE'S GATHERING INFORMATION
FOR WHO ?

413
00:32:34,282 --> 00:32:38,086
OUR COLLEAGUE WAS SUPPOSED TO
HAVE FIXED THE F.B.I. PROBLEM.

414
00:32:40,271 --> 00:32:44,225
YOU WILL FIX IT NOW.
DO YOU UNDERSTAND ME ?

415
00:32:44,225 --> 00:32:46,060
THEN I WILL FIX IT FOR GOOD.

416
00:33:59,350 --> 00:34:01,352
[ Blevins ]
AGENT MULDER,
WILL YOU PLEASE TAKE A SEAT ?

417
00:34:01,352 --> 00:34:04,272
SOMETHING URGENTLY IMPORTANT
HAS COME TO THE FORE.

418
